Titolo: Brix (video game)

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: Brix is a puzzle game for MS-DOS, developed by Michael Riedel and produced and published in 1991. An updated version with enhanced graphics & sound was published by Epic MegaGames in 1992. It is a clone of Taito's Puzznic, and thus bears strong graphical and some gameplay similarities to Flipull/Plotting, also produced by Taito. A deluxe version of the game titled Brix 2 Deluxe was released alongside the Epic MegaGames release, with dozens of new levels and a level editor.

Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: N/A
